text: Spyros Agrotis (; born 5 November 1961) is a Cypriot former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Cypriot male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Cyprus Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
